  "texts": [
    "Except for two single-sex studies 27, 61, all other studies recruited both sexes, with n = 139 (50.4%) females and n = 137 (49.6%) males across all the included studies.",
    "Characteristics of rehabilitation programs.",
    "In 8 (61.5%) of the 13 included studies 25, 27, [56] [57] [58] 62, 63, 65, the same setting of homebased VRehab program was provided to all study participants.",
    "However, in 5 (38.5%) of the included studies [59] [60] [61] 64, 66, participants were divided into two groups and received two different rehabilitation programs.",
    "Triantafyllidis et al."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
